tables.query: SELECT cache_hits, cache_lastuse, cache_state, client_connection, client_continent, client_country, client_timezone, gem, http2, platform, request, request_bytes, request_host, request_path, request_query, response_bytes, response_cache, response_status, response_text, server_datacenter, server_region, time_elapsed, timestamp, tls, tls_cipher, tls_version, user_agent, version FROM rubygems.downloads LIMIT 1000
